Layer 24 starts at 47² + 1 = 2210 at position (24, -23).

Working backwards in layer 23 from (23, -22):
The layer goes: right, up, left, down. Since 2026 is the first number (just moved right to start layer), (23, -23) is in the previous layer or doesn't exist yet in the spiral.

Actually, (23, -23) would be the last position before moving right to (24, -23). 
